<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5"> صحيح:</span> م <span class="c2">(٦/ ٨١)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>⦗٣٤٧⦘<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>قَالَ أَبُو حَاتِمٍ - رَضِيَ اللَّهُ عَنْهُ -: زَيْنَبُ: هِيَ بِنْتُ كَعْبِ بْنِ عُجْرَةَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>